name: No Mad Nomads
description:
A collection of 5000 (free!) Nomads who are really definitely no mad about the Nomad Bridge exploit, all stored and generated on-chain at the time of mint.  Collect your Nomad exploit memorabilia exclusively in this collection.

No twitter, discord, or social media of any kind. 

Thanks to https://twitter.com/Indelible_Labs for the contract and minting site. Also thanks to Chain Runners for use of their CC0 traits!
